#* {{quote-book|en|1936||Statistics of Land-grant Colleges and Universities|page=17|text=The status of academic school is conferred on any institution by a special law, and only academic schools are authorized to confer degrees and '''nostrify''' degrees granted Polish citizens abroad.}}
