# To [[adopt]], [[accept]], or [[include]] as part of one's own culture.
#* {{quote-journal|en|year=2000|||Indian journal of Secularism|volume=5|page=12|text=(We ''''nostrify'''' a certain opinion, accept it etc.) This means that the identity of the subject becomes enlarged.}}
