#* {{quote-book|en|2007|Benjamin Schliesser|Abraham's Faith in Romans 4|page=413|sction=footnote 164|text=Paul shows the Christian believers their place in the divine faith-righteousness, but does not "'''nostrify'''" Abraham in Christian terms.}}

